Access bank has disclosed that the DiamondXtra savings promo which is in its 10th year has given prizes worth over N5 billion in its lifespan. Speaking at the prize presentation held at Access bank’s office in Lagos yesterday, the Executive Director Retail Banking, Access Bank, Mr. Victor Etuokwu said the bank was rewarding its customers for their loyalty and patronage to the bank. Etuokwu said: “The product has been rewarding Nigerians of every gaps and there is no way the bank can add value to an economy and people without doing things like this a product of a bank must add value and DiamondXtra adds value every single day. “Over the last 10 and half years, over N5 billion have been given out and today.” Access Bank makes 10 millionaires at Diamondextra season 11 draw ‘Those who won ‘Salary for Life’ will keep it under Diamond, Access merger’ Can Access manage Intercontinental? Dear Esteemed reader, As part of our drive to keep improving the content of our newspaper, we are conducting a readership survey to enable us serve you better. Kindly take two minutes of your time to fill in this questionnaire. Thank you for your time. Click here to begin